bonding(绑定)是一种linux系统下的网卡绑定技术，可以把服务器上n个物理网卡在系统内部抽象(绑定)成一个逻辑上的网卡，能够提升网络吞吐量、实现网络冗余、负载均衡等功能，有很多优势。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">http://blog.ivps.top/post/ubuntu22.04-pei-zhi-shuang-wang-qia-bang-ding-ti-sheng-dai-kuan.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 11:51:25 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Ubuntu 使用Root用户SSH登录</title><link>http://blog.ivps.top/post/Ubuntu%20-shi-yong-Root-yong-hu-SSH-deng-lu.html</link><description>**1、安装openssh**&#13;
使用如下命令安装openssh&#13;
&#13;
sudo apt install openssh-server&#13;
&#13;
**2、修改配置文件sshd_config**&#13;
安装完成后修改配置文件/etc/ssh/sshd_config，命令如下&#13;
sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config&#13;
&#13;
将&#13;
&#13;
#PermitRootLogin prohibit-password&#13;
&#13;
改成&#13;
&#13;
PermitRootLogin yes&#13;
&#13;
**3、重启服务**&#13;
使用如下命令程序ssh服务&#13;
&#13;
sudo systemctl restart ssh。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">http://blog.ivps.top/post/Ubuntu%20-shi-yong-Root-yong-hu-SSH-deng-lu.html</guid><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 10:26:51 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Linux 命令</title><link>http://blog.ivps.top/post/Linux%20-ming-ling.html</link><description>Linux。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">http://blog.ivps.top/post/Linux%20-ming-ling.html</guid><pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 01:46:50 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>new test</title><link>http://blog.ivps.top/post/new%20test.html</link><description>newt 123。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">http://blog.ivps.top/post/new%20test.html</guid><pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 10:47:22 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>test</title><link>http://blog.ivps.top/post/test.html</link><description>123。</description><guid isPermaLink="true">http://blog.ivps.top/post/test.html</guid><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:10:46 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>